                            <comment id="15081439" author="beobal" created="Mon, 4 Jan 2016 17:41:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s a corner case which these patches don&apos;t cover. Namely, if &lt;tt&gt;data_file_directories&lt;/tt&gt; isn&apos;t set then the &lt;tt&gt;dir&lt;/tt&gt; argument to &lt;tt&gt;preVisitDirectory&lt;/tt&gt; is relative to &lt;tt&gt;bin&lt;/tt&gt; and so the &lt;tt&gt;Path&lt;/tt&gt; comparisons don&apos;t hold. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, in the 3.0 &amp;amp; trunk branches, &lt;tt&gt;Directories.SNAPSHOT_SUBDIR&lt;/tt&gt; is referenced twice in &lt;tt&gt;preVisitDirectory&lt;/tt&gt;, where the second time it should be &lt;tt&gt;Directories.BACKUP_SUBDIR&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve pushed branches with fixes for both issues, do they look reasonable to you &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=carlyeks&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;carlyeks&quot;&gt;carlyeks&lt;/a&gt; ?&lt;/p&gt;

